### Key Findings
1. V65 code diff: hub_penalty→network_penalty, expansion 5/30→10/60, retreat 15→20
2. Tournament uses 2+6/6+2/4+4 team splits (8 total agents, 10k steps)
3. Team-aware policies help locally but HURT in tournament
4. Zone targeting (sector assignment) best locally (3.63 avg) but scores 2.06 in tournament
5. Simple aggressive policies score better in tournament than sophisticated ones
6. Local self-play is NOT predictive of tournament performance

